                "name": "Internal Cauldron",
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "ability",
                "ability_type": "interaction",
                "text": "With an appropriate diet, an apothecary bee will create a potion of 6th level or lower every two weeks. Most often, this is a *moderate healing potion*. Each apothecary bee can store only one completed potion at a time. Unused potions can generally be harvested from an apothecary bee with a successful DC 23 Nature or Survival check.",
