            {
                "name": "Potionsight",
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "ability",
                "ability_type": "interaction",
                "text": "Apothecary bees' complex eyes let them see the auras of magical potions and instinctively identify potions of their level or lower. These auras are visible through mundane containers, though their eyes have no special ability to perceive or identify non-magical solutions, such as alchemical elixirs.",
                "links": [
